data.eml:eml: New species of Myrmosinae (Hymenoptera: Mutillidae) from Southeastern Asia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Williams, Kevin A., Lelej, Arkady S., Thaochan, Narit (2019): New species of Myrmosinae (Hymenoptera: Mutillidae) from Southeastern Asia. Zootaxa 4656 (3): 525-534, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4656.3.9
